        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【评测】Dyson OnTrac 纯正无线降噪耳机，用料质感上乘 + 实试降噪 + 重低音够震撼</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/dyson-ontrac-2/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=dyson-ontrac-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/dyson-ontrac-2/mobile-music/headphones/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 05 Aug 2024 03:00:25 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[影音产品]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[流动音乐]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[音乐耳机]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Dyson OnTrac]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1253985</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Dyson 耳机今次真的出了真功夫！今次他们发布 Dyson OnTrac 头戴式耳机产品，相比起 2023 年发布的 Dyson Zone，今次除去了空气净化单元，变成一对纯粹的降噪头戴式耳机。这款 Dyson OnTrac 利用了 Dyson 最先进的降噪技术，再加上 Dyson 的设计哲学，成为一款拥有时尚风格，而又实际有强劲降噪效果、音质佳的音乐耳机。小编近日就收到 Dyson 提供的街卖正式版耳机，以下同大家分享一下 Dyson OnTrac 的使用体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01417-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01417-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01417.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254012" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01462-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01462-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01462.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254014" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01450-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01450-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01450.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>耳机设计够「Dyson」质感高贵</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 是一款完全为音乐特化设计的头戴式无线降噪耳机。外型相当前衞，耳筒外壳利用全金属板制作，今次小编选择了 CNC 铝合金银色款，从外面看上去极为反光，很有「Dyson」的感觉。除此之外耳机柄身也用上全金属制作，每边耳机各设有一个开关按钮与一个十字掣操作按钮，按感非常实净，机身钢水绝对对得起耳机 4 千多元的售价。耳机头带与耳筒采用圆柱形多轴转向臂，令到 Dyson OnTrac 耳筒部份可轻松顺滑地 135 度转动，这种实净、顺滑的感觉也是这个级数的耳机才有。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254013" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01448-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01448-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01448.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01454-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01454-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01454.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254010" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01458-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01458-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01458.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254007" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01461-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01461-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01461.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Dyson OnTrac 的头带部份主要以金属设计，与头部接触的部份包裹布质尼龙提升质感。耳机巧妙将头带分成 3 部份。最顶部与头颅接触的部份用上软垫，佩戴时头部不会有被砸紧的感觉，而耳机电池则藏于头带另外与头部较少接触的部份。这个设计也将耳机重量放在头带位置，匀衡分配重重，令覆盖著耳朵的耳筒本体下坠感减低了很多。令到 Dyson OnTrac 耳机拿起上手感到有一定份量，但实际佩戴上去之后，会觉得比一般耳机更加舒服。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1254016" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01452-1-387x580.jpg" alt="" width="520" height="780" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01452-1-387x580.jpg 387w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01452-1.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 520px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254005" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01456-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01456-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01456.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01447-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01447-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01447.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Dyson OnTrac 的耳筒软垫也很讲究，表面细密绒面构造给予耳朵十分好的舒适感。只要调好耳机大小，耳机不会有太大夹耳的感觉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254004" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01418-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01418-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01418.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>可随意更换耳机外壳、耳棉，走出街可成时尚饰物</h2><p>整体来说 Dyson OnTrac 以质感上乘的材料，再加上结实的造工，令到整个耳机摸上手的质感，还有实际佩戴后的舒适程度，都有良好感受。特别一提的是 Dyson 将会为耳机提供不同种类的造型配搭，用户可自由配搭耳机外壳、耳棉款式，适合佩戴出街衬衫。耳机外壳提供 CNC 铝合金、CNC 铜合金、CNC 黑镍合金，以及陶瓷外壳， 目前官方建议零售价为每套 US$49.99（约港币$390，含一个外壳与一个软垫）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254006" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01460-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01460-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01460.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01446-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01446-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01446.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254020" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01463-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01463-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01463.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254021" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01465-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01465-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01465.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲保护套采用从顶部插入的方式设计，起初会觉得好奇怪，但如果是一般斜孭袋、公事包你可直接从顶部取出耳机，使用上意外地方便</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【实试】Dyson OnTrac 降噪耳机　主动降噪消除 40dB + 佩戴非常舒适</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>耳机听感丰富，三个设定适合收听不同声音内容</h2><p>在连接智能手机后，你马上可用来收听音乐、看 YouTube 甚至睇片。我们建议你再安装 MyDyson 手机应用程式。这里除可控制解噪效果外，更可设定均衡器。均衡器预设就有 3 个选择，包括增强音效、增强重低音，还有中性。你可马上找到哪个音色设定，能更符合你的口味。以下为大家分享这 3 个设定的不同听感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1209-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1209-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1209-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p>「增强音效」：同时将重低音、高音都加强演绎，特别适合收听具动感的音乐、睇 Netflix 看爆炸场面、收听挖耳的 ASMR，Dyson OnTrac 可带来非常震撼的效果，同时让高频声段同样清脆</p><p>「重低音」：Dyson OnTrac 的重低音本来已经很强劲，下潜力度强，但这个设定会令耳机以极限方式加强重低音效果，非常适合要极致重低音的朋友。Dyson OnTrac 特点是低频重低音效果做得非常震撼、下潜力足够，令到重低音不只有「量」，不是「呯呯」声响，而是具有质感、一种能像贯穿心脏的「Boom Boom」声。</p><p>「中性」：如果以 Dyson OnTrac 收听一般流行曲、慢歌，或者具有音乐性较重的音讯内容，就建议使用「中性」来加强人声的清晰度。</p><h2>降噪效果中上，可隔绝大部份城市噪音</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 变成一只纯音响耳机，但 Dyson 对于降噪方面仍然相当考究，耳机 ANC 主动降噪系统由 8 个咪高风组成，包括耳罩内都有咪高风，即使噪音穿过耳棉走进耳罩内，也能进行抵销。主动降噪系统将进行每秒 384,000 次的取样，官方声称可实行最大 40dB 的噪音去除。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253990" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01392-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01392-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01392.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253991" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01402-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01402-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01402.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>头戴式一般比更入耳式耳机更难处理降噪。当然我们也有实际测试。在交通量较为繁忙的街道上，小编特别走到巴士发动机后面。可发现就算在巴士引擎后方，收听歌曲或 YouTube 直播的人声都十分清晰。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253989" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01382-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01382-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01382.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而在巴士里面坐到底层后方，开启降噪功能后可除去绝大部份引擎声，再开启歌曲播放，即使是慢歌也很容易掩盖过余下的噪音，整体上非常实用。在佩戴 Dyson OnTrac 坐上一般交通工具，都可以放心听歌。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253988" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01380-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01380-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01380.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>实际听感－－超强劲力度的重低音，同时获得平衡</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 给小编第一个感觉，就是重低音效果相当强劲，它并不单只有大声量，其低频的下潜力十分强，具有圆润、结实而深沉的重低音演出而不会爆音，同时能够声音中频、高频的内容，能够清晰收听到，整体上给人满意的三频清晰度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253992" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01407-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01407-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01407.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳机下潜力佳的特性，令到用它来睇戏，或者收听 ASMR 等音效都很有临场感</p><p>有好多耳机在关闭耳机后才会得到最佳声线，但今次测试 Dyson OnTrac 发现它在降噪开动时已经很好声，尤其是在收听较有动感的歌曲。在收听 LiSA《Shouted Serenade》FLAC 24bit/48.0khz 无损音乐时，时我们将降噪调节到开启，均衡器开动「增强音效」，耳机可在以相当有「速度感」、力度去演绎音乐节拍，还有背景音乐，重点是背后的人声都清晰收听到。在节奏强劲的歌曲时，很多时面对耳机输出功率不足、「不够声」引致到低频下潜力不足，这款 Dyson OnTrac 就做到声线响亮有力，低频重量感也能确切体感得到。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253994" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01442-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01442-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01442.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>再试另一款同时重视人声与低频的歌曲，《MAISONdes 「なんもない feat. 星街すいせい, sakuma.」》FLAC 24bit/48.0kHz 无损音乐时，可发现到最初呈现出清晰人声，并且不会沉没于往后续渐变得大声的背景音乐，两者可清楚分离。音乐低频部份重厚有力，如果你还想再加强低频力度，可在「My Dyson」App 中再把均衡器设到「重低音」模式，这里可给你极为强力的重低音回响。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253993" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01440-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01440-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01440.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在实试听感的过程中，我们发现 Dyson OnTrac 有一样非常神奇的地方，是其降噪功能关掉后，耳机会变身一款更擅于演绎中频、高频的耳机，可说是拥有双重性格。在收听慢歌宇多田光《First Love (2022 Mix)》时开场时如果在「My Dyson」App 内设定均衡器到「中性」，人声会变得更为突出，音乐包括钢琴的声线会比较清脆，整体声线比较偏冷，你会收听到最多中、高频细节，而且音场也在中等以上的水平。如想要多点低频细节的话，将均衡器轻推到「增强音效」便可，这个设定也非常适合收听慢歌。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253995" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01444-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01444-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01444.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>实时显示耳内、环境音量，避免过大音量影响听力</h2><p>Dyson OnTrac 耳机内置有耳罩内感应器，除了可增强降噪效果之外，在「My Dyson」专用 App 内也利用到这个感应器，显示用户耳罩内的声量水平。用户可随时留意令自己不会曝露在高音量的环境下。小编实试在巴士高速走行的马路上，如不用降噪功能而用声量对抗的话，耳筒内音量可达 91dB，属于对耳产生不良影响的水平。耳科专家警告，如长时间收听 85dB 以上的大音量，将会造成听力受损。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01434-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01434-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01434.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲如不开降噪而强行加大音量去同噪音抗衡的话，耳筒内音量可随时轻易超过 90dB，属于对听力不健康的使用方法</p><p>如开启降噪功能，再将 iPhone 音量调节至约 80%，耳筒内声量约为 75dB，为相对较安全的水平。但也要留意即使是 75dB 的音量水平，也应避免长时间收听。在开启降噪之后，你甚至会看到图表显示耳筒中收听的声量比起外界环境噪音的声量还要低。证明了 Dyson OnTrac 今次虽然没有空气净化功能，不过降噪功能都可以帮你减低城市噪音对听力的影响（笑）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1224-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1224-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/img_1224-scaled.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1253999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01398-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01398-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01398.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【实试】Dyson OnTrac 降噪耳机　主动降噪消除 40dB + 佩戴非常舒适</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>总结：Dyson OnTrac 迎合一般音乐爱好者口味，值得一试</h2><p>在去年推出过 Dyson Zone 结合空气净化功能的耳机后，今次 Dyson 首次推出纯音乐耳机 Dyson OnTrac，纯粹以音乐效果、降噪功能作为主打。我们发现它的降噪功能属于中上水平，能够应对城市中大部份噪音，你更可在「My Dyson」App 里面随时留意耳机内的声音，与外部环境声量的差距，了解耳机给你的实际隔音、降噪的好处。而作为一款音乐耳机，Dyson OnTrac 给用我们的听感十分震撼，它能够掌握一般耳机在开启降噪功能后的特性，调节到具有重份量、下潜感十足、有力的低频效果之余，能同时兼顾到人声的演绎，非常适合收听节奏强劲流行曲。而将降噪功能关掉后，在家中你可体会到 Dyson OnTrac 清晰呈现清晰细腻音乐感的一面，整体来说这款耳机本身的潜力非常广阔。再加上这款耳机外观上「非常 Dyson」的设计、耳机本身的质感，耳机非常对得起它今次的售价，如果有机会的话大家也可以一试。</p><figure id="attachment_1254450" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1254450" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254450" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080212233-694x238.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="238" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080212233-694x238.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080212233.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1254450" class="wp-caption-text">▲今次 Dyson 总共推出 4 款不同外观的 Dyson OnTrac 耳机</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_1254451" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1254451" style="width: 694px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1254451" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080212242-694x323.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="323" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080212242-694x323.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/2024080212242.jpg 1032w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-1254451" class="wp-caption-text">▲用户可另外选购耳机壳+耳机垫套装，每套 HK$380</figcaption></figure><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1254017" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01451-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01451-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/dsc01451.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/18/dyson-ontrac/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【实试】Dyson OnTrac 降噪耳机　主动降噪消除 40dB + 佩戴非常舒适</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/05/dyson-ontrac-2/mobile-music/headphones/">【评测】Dyson OnTrac 纯正无线降噪耳机，用料质感上乘 + 实试降噪 + 重低音够震撼</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
